{"tid":2416661,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone用家比較蠢？研究：Android手機用家平均智商較高IQ達110.3","createTime":"2021-02-21T08:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T07:00:40.000Z","uid":4672,"like":34,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa6d45d48c4a0cdf935e2f52672951b97cf0884","tid":2416661,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213230/iphone%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E8%A0%A2-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-android%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%BC%83%E9%AB%98iq%E9%81%94110-3/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F213230%2Fiphone%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25BC%2583%25E8%25A0%25A2-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-android%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25BC%2583%25E9%25AB%2598iq%25E9%2581%2594110-3%2F2&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=48562719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213230/iphone%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E8%A0%A2-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-android%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%BC%83%E9%AB%98iq%E9%81%94110-3/2</a><br />\n<br />\n不少人常為Android 手機與 iPhone作出比較，最近外國線上賭場遊戲Royal Panda進行研究調查，針對iOS、Android、Windows、Mac等手機和電腦作業系統為研究，結果發現Android用戶平均智商較iPhone用戶高。<br />\nRoyal Panda早前與心理學家合作進行研究，針對iOS、Android、Windows、Mac等7 個平台，邀請到1001位用戶進行智商測驗，測驗內容包括語文、數學、邏輯與視覺等部分。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，<span class=\"orange\">Android 系統用戶的IQ平均分為110.3，而iPhone 用戶IQ平均分為102.1</span>，可見Android用家平均智商較高。而電腦系統方面情況相反，macOS用戶平均IQ為108.2 ，<span class=\"red\">比起平均IQ為106.7的Windows 用戶高</span>。<br />\n<br />\n雖然調查報告結果Android用家平均智商較高，但Royal Panda亦指用戶人數比例亦有機會拉低智商，加上測試方式也沒有詳細公佈，各位可以一笑置之不用太介懷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwindows用家躺槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592ddc58f4c365dd1daf8cc28798936281cdaacf","tid":2416661,"uid":4672,"like":37,"dislike":22,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"an9搵唔到嘢攻擊<br />\n唯有作文打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ab400d41059e884cd26af6e768ce397e3b7cd3","tid":2416661,"uid":66365,"like":21,"dislike":11,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">i</span>diot"},{"pid":"9ab6a855c5884b0a55d091abdff4841e272e0a6b","tid":2416661,"uid":346404,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話iphone好用。原來係佢地iq太低唔識用其他os"},{"pid":"8f4e41bd7ebd4243879254c6f4397528e9058580","tid":2416661,"uid":367723,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"原來窮人普遍智商高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：窮人"},{"pid":"97b9cb2bb45e3a225cf536ae951506b2bd8016ca","tid":2416661,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":16,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"iOS簡單易用，的確冇an機工程師咁叻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253c160d5c33ade7dd9bd55361900bb4dbcb3aec","tid":2416661,"uid":4672,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"97b9cb2bb45e3a225cf536ae951506b2bd8016ca","tid":2416661,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":16,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"iOS簡單易用，的確冇an機工程師咁叻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"an9: root機先係生活智慧 你識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461eef86b2818101a5898f363e5631f5c67d8753","tid":2416661,"uid":352851,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"又嚟講